---
title: Kale and Baby Corn Noodles  with Thai spices and lemongrass
description: Tender baby corn and carrot are familiar finds when it comes to veggie noodle dishes. A less-expected addition to this recipe comes in the form of crispy roasted kale—the leafy green that tops this moreish meal.
